COMMAND
  Place/Modify Light

VERSION
  2.0.1.0

TEST PROCEDURE

  Toggle reference plane display on in iso window
  Change ambient light (dark blue)
  Snapshot (db & si)
  Modify light 1 (green) 
  Update iso window
  Snapshot (db & si)

SNAPSHOT

  HSdpb2	current light number	last_light_num
		slider range	 	light_flags.HS_PLACE_LIGHT_SLIDER_RANGE	
		ambient light		amb_red, amb_green, amb_blue

  GRgraphics    light object		

  GRvg		light graphics
  

NOTES

  Invoking sub-form causes ppl to display shadow of main form instead.
  Can't test spot light
  
